t:
Two roads diverged in a wood, and I took the one less traveled by.


But when I realized that I didn't like that road, I went back and tried the other one.



People forget that they can do that.
c:
And if you don't like that road either, just go back to an earlier intersection.



#road #diverge #woods #travel #goback #retry #realization #forget





Failure is not the end, you just need to try again. Just don't regret and keep taking the same road over and over again.
